This package intentionally does not vendor SkywarnPlus, HBLink3, Analog_Bridge,
MMDVM_Bridge, md380-emu, or any proprietary AMBE implementation.

The direct OpenBridge packetizer uses the public HomeBrew/OpenBridge packet layout
and depends on dmr-utils3 for DMR link-control/FEC construction when direct DMR
packet generation is enabled. dmr-utils3 and HBLink3 are GPL-family projects; keep
this package GPL-compatible if you redistribute modified versions.
